est with Bill Ackman, and have put their names on a nonbinding list that wi=
ll let them do so.But I also want to emphasize that this pitch is also the =
same as =E2=80=A6 nothing? Like if Chamath Palihapitiya =E2=80=94=C2=A0or B=
ill Ackman for that matter =E2=80=94=C2=A0found some nice private company a=
