ARC it=E2=80=99s not because the SPARC has money to give you, it=E2=80=99s =
because you are confident that Bill Ackman can=C2=A0go find=C2=A0money to g=
ive you.Anyway, like I said, this is only one of the things that Pershing S=
quare Tontine Holdings is doing. PSTH is a SPAC (not a SPARC) that Bill Ack=
man launched=C2=A0way back in July 2020; he raised $4 billion to  hunt for =
(in his words) a =E2=80=9CMature Unicorn.=E2=80=9D PSTH did not find a Matu=
re Unicorn. PSTH is, however, a rather Mature SPAC at this point: Like all =
SPACs, it has a two-year deadline to do a deal, and the clock started runni=
ng last July. That still gives it more than a year, but =E2=80=9Cstartups t=
