 weird way:PSTH will satisfy its shareholders=E2=80=99 redemption rights by=
 tendering for its shares at a price equal to PSTH=E2=80=99s cash-in-trust =
per-share, or approximately $20 per share (the =E2=80=9CRedemption Tender O=
ffer=E2=80=9D). The Redemption Tender Offer is expected to be launched shor=
