e chooses the first option =E2=80=94=C2=A0to exchange their warrants for mo=
re shares =E2=80=94=C2=A0then, in effect, the warrants vanish. Every shareh=
older goes from owning 1 share of PSTH to owning 1.09 shares or whatever,[5=
